be dark with smoke.

00:39:22.470 --> 00:39:25.950
And after you finish cooking,
your clothes will stink.

00:39:25.950 --> 00:39:29.900
You cannot even serve the food
without taking a shower before.

00:39:29.900 --> 00:39:32.990
So I was relaxed.

00:39:32.990 --> 00:39:38.080
And I could cook with dignity,
even in my nice clothes,

00:39:38.080 --> 00:39:40.730
using an InStove--
which is not possible

00:39:40.730 --> 00:39:42.442
with a three-stone
cooking fire method.

00:39:45.280 --> 00:39:47.480
